  "title": "Production Operator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Principal Accountabilities</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Safety</strong></p>\n<p>· Perform work in accordance to safety requirements at all times.</p>\n<p>· Ensure all Safety-guards are in placed before operating equipment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Operational</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate equipment in accordance to Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) and Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n  <li>Perform setup and configuration of equipment to work-on film and paper product reels</li>\n  <li>Perform proper recording of product information before and after processing</li>\n  <li>Perform visual inspection of product to detect defects as identified by SOP and WIs</li>\n  <li>Perform re-work of product as instructed by Leadership</li>\n  <li>Perform proper hand-over take-over to/from shift co-workers</li>\n  <li>Perform proper sample taking/marking/recording of samples at specific interval per SOP and Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n  <li>Perform proper product packaging per SOP and Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n  <li>Print core labels/pallet labels and ensure proper labelling of reels as per Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n  <li>Perform equipment maintenance as per Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n  <li>Notify Leadership/QA Engineer if any additional defects found</li>\n  <li>Ensure General 5S housekeeping of work area / machine cleaning</li>\n  <li>Move and Feed production material per Work Instructions (WIs)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Others</strong></p>\n<p>• To help-out in other areas of production such as Finished Goods Packing and Retrieving of Materials from the Warehouse as and when needed.</p>\n<p>• Other Ad hoc assignments</p>",
